##SublimeText3 安装过程：
 下载：sublime下载网址：https://www.sublimetext.com/3
        PackageControl：https://github.com/wbond/package_control

   方法一：##下载完成后，找到下载的文件，解压，将文件夹重命名为“Package Control”复制到sublime存放插件的目录 
   [网站](https://blog.csdn.net/wuyou1336/article/details/78966337)
   启动sublime：点击状态栏:Preferences > Package Settings > Package Control > Settings - User

   方法二：解压好sublime后复制Package Control.sublime-package文件到SublimeText3\Data\Installed Packages文件夹下
   		****注意：是Package Control.sublime-package而不是Package Control.sublime-packages等等
   

   		User文件下添加
{
	"bootstrapped": true,
	"channels":
	[
		"http://cst.stu.126.net/u/json/cms/channel_v3.json"//或者：http://static.zybuluo.com/parkinwu/x5xsu1vjaob4hmktfexncfbz/channel_v3.json
	],
	"in_process_packages":
	[
	],
	"installed_packages":
	[
		"1337 Color Scheme",
		"ChineseLocalizations",
		"Package Control"
	]
}


   解决Sublime的package control被墙:https://blog.csdn.net/jyfu2_12/article/details/86667132
   解决安装插件不成：https://blog.csdn.net/csdn_yudong/article/details/84866428
